{"fixed_xml":"<ITEM>
  In denen Thurneysischen Buchl
	lden allhier, seynd dato folgende zwey B
	cher zu haben, so in Nancy durch Subscriptiones gedruckt worden.
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Dictionnaire Universel- Francois & Latin, Vulgairement appell
	 Dictionaire de Trevoux</TITLE>
    avec des Remarques d Erudition & de Critique
    <VOLUME>5. Tom.</VOLUME>
    <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
    <YEAR>1741</YEAR>
    ; davon die 3. ersten Tom. dato schon zu beziehen sind; das gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht
    <PRICE>fl. 24</PRICE>
  </BIBL>
  .
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Dictionaire Oeconomique, continant les moyens d'Augmenter son dien & de conserver sa sante</TITLE>
    , par
    <AUTHOR>Mister Noel Chomel</AUTHOR>
    , Augmente dun Nouveau Supplement de deur Volumes, par
    <AUTHOR>F. Marset, Doct. en Medecines</AUTHOR>
    .
    <FORMAT>2vec fig.</FORMAT>
    <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME>
    <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
    <YEAR>1741</YEAR>
    ; davon der erste Tomus dato bey ihnen zu beziehen ist; di
	 gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht
    <PRICE>fl. 18</PRICE>
  </BIBL>
  .
  So dann sind bey ihnen auch genugsam annoch zu haben:
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Dictionaire Historique & Critique de Mr. Bayle</TITLE>
    -
    <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME>
    <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
    <PLACE>Amsterd.</PLACE>
    <YEAR>1740</YEAR>
    .
    <PRICE>L. 27</PRICE>
  </BIBL>
  .
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Corpus Juris Civilis Romani, cum Notis Gotofrest</TITLE>
    <VOLUME>2. Tom.</VOLUME>
    <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
    <YEAR>1740</YEAR>
    .
    <PRICE>fl. 10. 48. xr.</PRICE>
  </BIBL>
  .
  <BIBL>
    <TITLE>Dictionaire Royal, Francois-Allemand-Latin, par le R. P. Fr. Pomey</TITLE>
    <VOLUME>3. Voll.</VOLUME>
    <FORMAT>4to</FORMAT>
    <YEAR>1741</YEAR>
    .
    <PRICE>fl. 5. 24. xr.</PRICE>
  </BIBL>
</ITEM>","number_of_corrections":5,"explanation":"The XML was corrected to be well-formed. Primarily, the ampersands were escaped as &. The closing ITEM tag was added.  The abbreviation 4\u221a\u2264 was changed to 4to as it seems that was the intended meaning. Closing tags were also added."}
